## Extension Functions

### Keep Extensions Organized
```kotlin
// ✅ GOOD - extension at bottom of file
private fun User.mapToUI() = UserUI(
    id = this.id,
    name = this.name
)

private fun List<User>.mapToUI() = this.map { it.mapToUI() }

// ✅ GOOD - separate extension file for shared functions
// File: extensions/UserExtensions.kt
fun User.displayName() = "$firstName $lastName"
```

### Scope Extension Functions Carefully
```kotlin
// ✅ GOOD - private extensions in ViewModel
private fun Item.mapToUI() = ItemUI(...)

// ❌ AVOID - public extensions everywhere
fun Item.mapToUI() = ItemUI(...)  // Pollutes global namespace
```

