## Resource Management

### Use Lazy Initialization
```kotlin
// ✅ GOOD - lazy initialization
private val database: MyDatabase by lazy {
    Room.databaseBuilder(context, MyDatabase::class.java, "db").build()
}

// ❌ BAD - eager initialization in init block
private lateinit var database: MyDatabase

init {
    database = Room.databaseBuilder(...).build()
}
```

### DisposableEffect for Cleanup
```kotlin
// ✅ GOOD - cleanup on exit
DisposableEffect(Unit) {
    val observer = LifecycleEventObserver { _, event ->
        if (event == ON_START) viewModel.load()
    }
    lifecycle.addObserver(observer)
    onDispose {
        lifecycle.removeObserver(observer)
    }
}
```

