## Naming Conventions (Recap)

| Type | Style | Example |
|------|-------|---------|
| Class | PascalCase | `MyFeatureViewModel` |
| Function/Property | camelCase | `fetchUserData()`, `isLoading` |
| Constant | UPPER_CASE | `const val MAX_ITEMS = 10` |
| Private/Internal | Prefix underscore | `_uiState`, `_error` |
| Interface (optional) | PascalCase | `MyRepository` |
| Enum value | UPPER_CASE | `STATE_LOADING` |

