## When/If Expressions

### Prefer Expression Over Statement
```kotlin
// ✅ GOOD - expression assignment
val message = when (status) {
    LOADING -> "Loading..."
    SUCCESS -> "Done!"
    ERROR -> "Error!"
}

val canProceed = if (isValid) true else false

// ❌ BAD - statement assignment
val message: String
when (status) {
    LOADING -> message = "Loading..."
    SUCCESS -> message = "Done!"
    ERROR -> message = "Error!"
}
```
